- You want a single synthesized article-style answer (overview → prerequisites → core → related), not a flat list of nugget blocks.
- User asks about Chia blockchain concepts: consensus, farming, plots, pooling, timelord, full node, wallet sync
- Chialisp, CLVM, opcodes, currying, standard puzzles, P2 conditions, AGG_SIG, announcements
- CATs, offers, NFTs, DID, custody, asset issuance, wallet SDK, driver layers
